  "_aboutBody": {
    "value": "Since opening our doors in 1964, Duran's Station has been a cornerstone of the Albuquerque community, founded by the Duran family with a passion for authentic New Mexican cuisine. What started as a small, beloved local eatery has grown into a cherished tradition, known for our homemade red and green chile and a welcoming atmosphere that makes every guest feel like family. We're proud to continue our legacy, serving up time-honored recipes passed down through generations.",
    "source": "qa_fix"
  }
